{
  "id": "699e8d3ff4a799761d7cd398",
  "title": "Spotify APIで遊ぼう",
  "created": 1771998530,
  "updated": 1772066924,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "699e8d3ff4a799761d7cd398",
      "text": "Spotify APIで遊ぼう",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1771998530,
      "updated": 1771998533
    },
    {
      "id": "699e8d450000000000a8bdf2",
      "text": "　Spotify APIを使って何か遊べないか模索中[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1771998533,
      "updated": 1771998632
    },
    {
      "id": "699e8d8f0000000000a8bdf7",
      "text": "　https://developer.spotify.com/documentation/web-api",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1771998607,
      "updated": 1771998627
    },
    {
      "id": "699e8d4f0000000000a8bdf4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1771998544,
      "updated": 1771998544
    },
    {
      "id": "699e8e110000000000a8bdf9",
      "text": "見た感じ面白そうな機能",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1771998737,
      "updated": 1771998740
    },
    {
      "id": "699e8d4f0000000000a8bdf5",
      "text": "　楽曲成分機能",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1771998544,
      "updated": 1771998737
    },
    {
      "id": "699e8e0c0000000000a8bdf8",
      "text": "　\tSpotify側で楽曲の成分分析用の指標があり、各曲はパラメーターによって分類される。",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1771998732,
      "updated": 1771998741
    },
    {
      "id": "699e8d7d0000000000a8bdf6",
      "text": "　\t\t内部的にはこれで楽曲のおすすめ機能やラジオ機能と紐づいているっぽい？",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1771998589,
      "updated": 1771998742
    },
    {
      "id": "699e8e170000000000a8bdfa",
      "text": "\tユーザー情報取得",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1771998743,
      "updated": 1771998749
    },
    {
      "id": "699f986c0000000000a08297",
      "text": "\t",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1772066924,
      "updated": 1772066924
    },
    {
      "id": "699e8e190000000000a8bdfb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1771998746,
      "updated": 1771998746
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef22f000000000027ac5c",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024368,
      "updated": 1772024368
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef230000000000027ac5e",
      "text": " [hoagecko.icon]は開発者としてではなくユーザーとしてSpotify APIを使うSelfhosted系のアプリを使っていた",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024369,
      "updated": 1772024565
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef24f000000000027ac5f",
      "text": " Your Spotify",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024399,
      "updated": 1772024408
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef278000000000027ac62",
      "text": " \t[Yooooomi/your_spotify: Self hosted Spotify tracking dashboard https://github.com/Yooooomi/your_spotify]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024440,
      "updated": 1772024441
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef258000000000027ac60",
      "text": " \t再生統計のダッシュボード",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024409,
      "updated": 1772024418
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef262000000000027ac61",
      "text": " spotify_player",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024419,
      "updated": 1772024450
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef2b6000000000027ac67",
      "text": " \t[aome510/spotify-player: A Spotify player in the terminal with full feature parity https://github.com/aome510/spotify-player]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024503,
      "updated": 1772024504
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef283000000000027ac63",
      "text": " \tRust製のCLIプレイヤー",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024451,
      "updated": 1772024462
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef28e000000000027ac64",
      "text": " \t実は音質が他と結構違う(rodio_backend)",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024463,
      "updated": 1772024920
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef2a0000000000027ac66",
      "text": "\tMulti-Scrobbler",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024481,
      "updated": 1772024535
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef2d0000000000027ac68",
      "text": "\t\t[Spotify | Multi-Scrobbler https://foxxmd.github.io/multi-scrobbler/configuration/sources/spotify/]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024529,
      "updated": 1772024531
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef2d8000000000027ac69",
      "text": "\t\t最強Scrobbler",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024537,
      "updated": 1772024541
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef3a8000000000027ac6b",
      "text": "\t[Update on Developer Access and Platform Security | Spotify for Developers https://developer.spotify.com/blog/2026-02-06-update-on-developer-access-and-platform-security]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024744,
      "updated": 1772024745
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef3a9000000000027ac6c",
      "text": "\t\tなんか最近APIの制限が厳しくなったらしいのでそれからは怖くてこれらのソフトを触っていない",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024746,
      "updated": 1772024935
    },
    {
      "id": "699ef230000000000027ac5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1772024368,
      "updated": 1772024368
    }
  ]
}